Hexagon Box

avatar -{{user}} needs a background image defined in _hexagon-box.scss if statements are just for styleguide. In production just use -white -djtb classes etc

 
<div class="hexagon-box -white">
	<a href="//github.com/[object Object]" class="inner">
		<div class="avatar -[object Object]"></div>
	</a>
</div>
